metadata.name: 2021 Graphic Art Project - The Way to The Star
metadata.title: 2021 Graphic Art Project - The Way to The Star
metadata.author: 雪栗 Cheri
metadata.description: The little fox and the lion embark on a journey to find the stars. Just like their stories, your journey is just beginning, don't worry about getting lost or falling because that shining star will be waiting for you at the end of the night.
